      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for an experienced mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated project car. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a non-functional transmission and an engine that requires a complete overhaul to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear with several dents, failing clear coat, and some surface rust, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and non-working electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend towing it from the lot.",
