    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this meticulously preserved specimen. Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of mechanical and aesthetic quality. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this is an unrivaled opportunity to acquire a truly pristine, investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48900.0,
